rows.label: qst200603_0010
rows.name: So, is this really the place?

rows.label: qst200603_0020
rows.name:
Well... From what the soldiers said,
it should be around here somewhere...

rows.label: qst200603_0030
rows.name:
You really think a great demon's gonna
show up in this deserted place?

rows.label: qst200603_0040
rows.name:
Don't act like this is my fault!
How am I meant to know?

rows.label: qst200603_0050
rows.name:
If there've been sightings, that means there
has to be SOMETHING here, right?

rows.label: qst200603_0070
rows.name: Something appear!

rows.label: qst200603_0080
rows.name: Is that...the demon?

rows.label: qst200603_0090
rows.name: It's huge...

rows.label: qst200603_0100
rows.name:
Even for a demon, isn't that
a bit too massive?

rows.label: qst200603_0110
rows.name: It incredible!

rows.label: qst200603_0120
rows.name: Kubira!

rows.label: qst200603_0130
rows.name: Hold on!

rows.label: qst200603_0140
rows.name: So, you are the foul demon?

rows.label: qst200603_0150
rows.name:
You are insolent indeed
to look down on my personage.

rows.label: qst200603_0160
rows.name: But no matter.

rows.label: qst200603_0170
rows.name:
Not all can be as versed in proper conduct as I.
I will grant you an audience.

rows.label: qst200603_0180
rows.name:
Hold on - what are you, stupid?
You're just gonna go face that thing?

rows.label: qst200603_0190
rows.name: Seriously - you'll be crushed to pieces!

rows.label: qst200603_0200
rows.name: Do you hear my voice, demon?!

rows.label: qst200603_0210
rows.name: I am king of a land named Rigideria!

rows.label: qst200603_0220
rows.name:
I know you are the beast that
caused my kingdom's downfall.

rows.label: qst200603_0230
rows.name:
As King, I must avenge my people
whom you wronged long ago!

rows.label: qst200603_0240
rows.name: If you are truly as terrible as the legends say...

rows.label: qst200603_0250
rows.name:
Then show me the extent of your strength!
Show me the power that felled a kingdom!

rows.label: qst200603_0260
rows.name: Quit provoking that thing already, Kubira!

rows.label: qst200603_0270
rows.name:
Actually, does that creature even
understand human speech?

rows.label: qst200603_0280
rows.name:
Why so shy, demon?
Do you not wish to do battle?

rows.label: qst200603_0290
rows.name: Hmm... Then let's see how you like this!

rows.label: qst200603_0300
rows.name: Meh-meh! What Kubira doing?!

rows.label: qst200603_0310
rows.name:
Ahahahaha... So, demon.
At last you recognize your foe.

rows.label: qst200603_0320
rows.name:
"At last you recognize your foe"?!
You moron, Kubira!

rows.label: qst200603_0330
rows.name: Now you've gone and really made it mad!

rows.label: qst200603_0340
rows.name: Why would you provoke it?

rows.label: qst200603_0350
rows.name: You ask strange questions, girl.

rows.label: qst200603_0360
rows.name:
For what purpose did we come here
if not to fell this foul beast?

rows.label: qst200603_0370
rows.name:
That's no reason to get it all worked up!
Haven't you heard of careful strategy?!

rows.label: qst200603_0380
rows.name: Dear me...

rows.label: qst200603_0390
rows.name:
Can you truly be so afraid of a mere animal?
And you call yourselves my retainers!

rows.label: qst200603_0400
rows.name: That's not the issue here, moron!

rows.label: qst200603_0410
rows.name:
We've landed ourselves in a right pickle.
What do we do now, Rex?

rows.label: qst200603_0420
rows.name: What now?

rows.label: qst200603_0430
rows.name: Best to retreat...

rows.label: qst200603_0440
rows.name:
Then we find Superbian Divine Beast warship
to help us take demon down!

rows.label: qst200603_0450
rows.name: Hopeless, every one of you.

rows.label: qst200603_0460
rows.name:
Wait here awhile, retainers.
I will slay the demon myself.

rows.label: qst200603_0470
rows.name: You, hold my sword.

rows.label: qst200603_0480
rows.name: You'll die, you know.

rows.label: qst200603_0490
rows.name:
I will not. Nay, I cannot.
For the people of Rigideria, I must prevail.

rows.label: qst200603_0500
rows.name: Okay then. I'm convinced. Let's do this.

rows.label: qst200603_0510
rows.name: You're really sure about this, Rex?

rows.label: qst200603_0520
rows.name:
All right, then...
I guess there's no point arguing with you.

rows.label: qst200603_0530
rows.name: Let's go slay that moron's demon.
